---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
	title="Skills"
	description="Skilll and technology stack that I have learned and used in my projects."
	keywords="code contributions,developer advocate, open source collaboration, problem solver, software development, laravel developer, react developer, full stack developer, javascript developer, web developer, software engineer"
	image="/favicon.svg"
>
	<section>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="content">
				<h1>Skills and technologies</h1>
				<div class="grid">
					<ul>
						<h2>FrontEnd:</h2>
						<li>Javascript/Typescript</li>
						<li>Bootstrap</li>
						<li>TailwindCSS</li>
						<li>jQuery</li>
						<li>Astro (this website was built with it)</li>
						<li>Vue.js</li>
						<li>Nuxt.js</li>
						<li>React.js</li>
						<li>SvelteKit</li>
						<li>Electron.js</li>
					</ul>
					<ul>
						<h2>BackEnd:</h2>
						<li>Golang</li>
						<li>PHP (Laravel, Lumen, Codeigniter)</li>
						<li>Node.js (Express.js, Adonis.js, Nest.js)</li>
						<li>
							Databases (PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB, Microsoft SQL Server, Redis, Supabase, SQLite)
						</li>
					</ul>
					<ul>
						<h2>DevOps:</h2>
						<li>Nginx (Reverse Proxy, Load Balancer, Cache, SSL, Rate Limiting)</li>
						<li>PM2</li>
						<li>Laravel Octane (Swoole, FrankenPHP)</li>
						<li>CI/CD & Version Control (GIT, GitHub, Gitlab, Jenkins)</li>
						<li>HashiCorp Vault</li>
						<li>Configuration & Automation (Ansible, Docker, Podman, Dokploy)</li>
						<li>Monitoring & Observability (Prometheus, Grafana, Sentry, Netdata)</li>
						<li>Cloud Platforms (AWS, Azure, Google Cloud Platform, Cloudflare R2)</li>
					</ul>
					<ul>
						<h2>Web Scraping & Automation</h2>
						<li>Selenium</li>
						<li>Puppeteer</li>
						<li>Appium</li>
						<li>Python</li>
						<li>N8N</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	section {
		padding-bottom: 30px;
	}
	div {
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}
	.grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-gap: 1rem;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
	}
	@media screen and (max-width: 640px) {
		.grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
	.grid li {
		flex: 50%;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
	}
	ul {
		margin-left: 30px;
	}
</style>
